Package: MethylationTuples
Type: Package
Title: Tools for analysing methylation patterns at genomic tuples
Version: 0.4.0.9001
Date: 2015-10-14
Authors@R: c(person("Peter", "Hickey", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "peter.hickey@gmail.com"))
Author: Peter Hickey <peter.hickey@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Peter Hickey <peter.hickey@gmail.com>
Description: MethylationTuples provides tools for analysing, managing and
    visualising methylation patterns at genomic tuples. These include analyses
    of co-methylation and epipolymorphism.
URL: www.github.com/PeteHaitch/MethylationTuples
BugReports: https://github.com/PeteHaitch/MethylationTuples/issues
biocViews: DNAMethylation, DataImport, Software, MethylSeq
VignetteBuilder: knitr
